title: L'Oiseau Cabosse
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Beer/Wine, French, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A popular brunch place on a quiet street alongside other restaurants. Around half of the menu is vegetarian suitable. You pick 1 or 2 options to make up a main course. Uses local organic products whenever possible and also sell a few organic products. Young crowd atmosphere with music playing.
